        {
            "title": "Elliott力促倫敦證券交易所集團剝離資產並回購50億英鎊股票",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Elliott力促倫敦證券交易所集團剝離資產並回購50億英鎊股票\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OoXQQ.kWOzqjTZdGUVOjVA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-07/5cd981c0-5f31-11f0-9fdf-36c2fad7d501\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Elliott力促倫敦證券交易所集團剝離資產並回購50億英鎊股票</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/elliott%E5%8A%9B%E4%BF%83%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E8%AD%89%E5%88%B8%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%89%80%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98%E5%89%9D%E9%9B%A2%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2%E4%B8%A6%E5%9B%9E%E8%B3%BC50%E5%84%84%E8%8B%B1%E9%8E%8A%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8-200419277.html",
